original_title: Ring Roasts II: A Comical Tribute to Terry Funk
overview: Pro Wrestling's most unpredictable, hilarious, wild event is back!  LAUGHTER... Comics and wrestlers alike go wild and uncensored on the Funker, and each other!  TEARS... The sanctity of friendship and life itself.  DANGER... Anything can happen at Ring Roasts... and usually does!  Starring: Terry Funk, Mick Foley, Superstar Billy Graham, New Jack, Kevin Sullivan, Bill Apter, Kevin Von Erich, Mike Graham, King Kong Bundy, J.J. Dillon, Missy Hyatt, Dennis Stamp, Ryan Maher, Sean Morton, Matt Bridgestone.
title: Ring Roasts II: A Comical Tribute to Terry Funk
